    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, she's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It drives like a dream and is perfect for someone who wants a quality ride without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see how great it feels behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
