      "description": "This vehicle represents an exceptional opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, aesthetically pleasing car that has been treated with care. The exterior finish maintains a high gloss, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips from highway use, and is completely free of major dents or deep scratches. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats are supportive with no tears or heavy bolster wear, and it has been kept strictly smoke-free. All interior technology, including the infotainment system, backup camera, and heated seats, functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, reflecting a documented history of regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. With plenty of tread remaining on the tires and a recent brake service, this car is ready for the road immediately. It is a solid, honest example of a well-loved vehicle that offers many years of dependable service ahead.",
      "price": 34500.0,
