      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable gem for me! It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s ready to hit the road without a hitch, this is the one. I\u2019ve taken care of all the basics so you can just hop in and enjoy the drive. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home!",
